hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: How would you like the money? roar physiotherapy Later I went out with my friend, who has been biking seriously for the past year, and we did a 20-miler. He went out of my comfort zone the whole way and did loops so I could catch up. I was completely demoralised. And then, getting to the 20-mile mark, I got a puncture and had to call my wife to rescue me. I have a puncture repair kit, pump and spare tyre but I need someone to teach me how to use them.
